# Keep the published pub.dev package lean: ship only lib/, bin/, example/, and
# the top-level docs (README, LICENSE, CHANGELOG). Everything below is either a
# development/test artifact, vendored reference material, or planning state that
# consumers of the pure-Dart library never need.

# Tests and their fixtures.
test/
dart_test.yaml

# C++ golden-frame harness (CMake mock server) and vendored reference sources.
test_harness/
third_party/

# GSD planning artifacts and repo-development instructions.
.planning/
CLAUDE.md

# CI configuration and coverage output.
.github/
coverage/

# Test-parity audit — a development artifact, not a consumer-facing doc.
PARITY.md
